<p><strong>Key Takeaways</strong></p>



<ul>
<li>Double&nbsp;&#8211; checking transaction details&nbsp;before sending any cryptocurrency can prevent irreversible loss of funds</li>



<li>Contacting the recipient or wallet provider/exchange is a viable option if you accidentally sent your Bitcoin to the wrong address</li>



<li>Seeking assistance from reputable recovery services and professionals&nbsp;with experience in crypto recovery may increase the chances of recovering lost funds</li>
